<title>ḥb ktyr ạlshryẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ḥb ktyr ạlshryẗ kl lyl mʿ ạlmsyḥ
 lw mạ nḥkyth ʿly ʿn drbh msẖ mmkn zyḥ
 1- ḥbh ḥbh ktyr wbạqwl hw ạldnyạ ʿhdh ạ̉dẖkr
 wạlkẖṭyỷẗ ạ̉dysẖ mkẖjwl lmạ byjynạ ạlmsyḥ
 2- mạ ạ̉ḥly̱ yswʿ rby ṣwrth mḥfwrẗ bqlby
 yạ nạs ạ̉nạ sẖw drby hdẖạ ạlṭryq ạlṣḥyḥ
 3- bạṭlb mnk yạ rby dl rfạqy ʿ drby
 wạ̹nt tqwy ly qlby bhạ ạlạ̹ymạn ạlṣḥyḥ
 4- ḥbh qd mnạ ʿywny ạ̉rjwkm lạ tlwmwny
 mhmạ ạ̹ntm dʿtwny ʿn ḥbh msẖ mmkn zyḥ</lyrics>
</song>